{"id":101,"date":"2026-03-27T03:36:30","date_gmt":"2026-03-27T03:36:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/fixmytyrenow.com\/?page_id=101"},"modified":"2026-03-27T03:36:30","modified_gmt":"2026-03-27T03:36:30","slug":"about","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/fixmytyrenow.com\/about\/","title":{"rendered":"About"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">About FixMyTyreNow<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Who We Are<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>FixMyTyreNow was built with one clear mission: to make tyre emergencies, roadside breakdowns, and routine tyre replacements fast, simple, and completely stress-free across London.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We understand that dealing with a flat tyre or damaged wheel is never convenient. It happens when you are rushing to work, picking up your children, or heading to an important meeting. That is why we created a fully mobile tyre service that comes directly to you, wherever you are.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We are not just another tyre company. We are a response-driven, customer-focused service designed for modern drivers who value speed, reliability, and transparency.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our team consists of experienced tyre technicians who have worked across roadside assistance, garages, and fleet services. We combined that real-world experience with a smarter, more efficient service model that eliminates the need for towing, waiting rooms, or unnecessary delays.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What We Do<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We provide a complete range of mobile tyre services across London, available when and where you need them.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our core services include:<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Emergency tyre replacement<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Puncture repair<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Run-flat tyre replacement<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Mobile tyre fitting<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Wheel balancing<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Roadside assistance for flat tyres<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Home, workplace, and roadside service<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Whether you are stuck on the roadside or simply prefer the convenience of having tyres fitted at your home or office, we bring the solution directly to you.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Why FixMyTyreNow Exists<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Traditional garages are outdated for today\u2019s lifestyle. They require:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Time-consuming appointments<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Travel to and from the location<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Long waiting times<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Unclear pricing<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>We saw a gap in the market and built FixMyTyreNow to remove all of that friction.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our service is designed around three simple principles:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. Speed<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We respond quickly and aim to get you back on the road as soon as possible.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. Convenience<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We come to your location. No towing. No waiting rooms. No disruption to your day.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. Transparency<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Clear pricing, honest advice, and no unnecessary upselling.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Service Areas<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We operate across Greater London, covering:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Central London<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>North London<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>East London<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>West London<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>South London<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Our mobile units are strategically positioned to reduce response times and ensure we can reach customers quickly, no matter where they are located.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Who We Help<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our services are designed for a wide range of customers:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Individual Drivers<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Daily commuters<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Families<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ride-share drivers<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Delivery drivers<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Business &amp; Corporate Clients<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Fleet operators<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Logistics companies<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Car rental businesses<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Corporate offices with company vehicles<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>We understand that downtime costs money. That is why our service is built to minimise disruption and keep vehicles moving.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Corporate Subscription Model<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For businesses that rely on vehicles every day, we offer a flexible subscription-based mobile tyre service.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This model is designed specifically for companies that need ongoing, reliable tyre support without the hassle of managing multiple service providers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Key benefits of our subscription service:<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Priority response times<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Dedicated account management<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Predictable monthly costs<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>On-site tyre maintenance and replacement<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Reduced vehicle downtime<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Scalable plans based on fleet size<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Instead of reacting to problems, businesses can proactively manage tyre health and avoid costly disruptions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How Our Service Works<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We have made the process simple and efficient.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 1: Book Online or Call<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Enter your location, vehicle details, and service required.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 2: We Come to You<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Our technician is dispatched to your location with the right equipment and tyres.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 3: Fast On-Site Service<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We repair or replace your tyre on the spot.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 4: Back on the Road<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>No towing, no delays, no unnecessary hassle.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Commitment to Quality<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We do not cut corners when it comes to safety and quality.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">We ensure:<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>High-quality tyres from trusted brands<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Professional-grade equipment<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fully trained technicians<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Safe and compliant repair standards<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Your safety on the road is our priority, and every job we complete reflects that responsibility.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What Makes Us Different<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There are many tyre services in London, but very few operate the way we do.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Here is what sets FixMyTyreNow apart:<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Fully mobile service across London<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fast response times<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Transparent pricing<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>No need for towing<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Convenient booking process<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Corporate subscription model for businesses<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>We are built for speed, reliability, and customer satisfaction.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Frequently Asked Questions<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How quickly can you reach me?<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Our response time depends on your location and traffic conditions, but we aim to reach most customers as quickly as possible within London.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Do I need to know my tyre size?<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>No. If you are unsure, our team can help identify the correct tyre based on your vehicle.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Can you repair any puncture?<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Not all punctures can be safely repaired. If the damage is within repairable limits, we will fix it. Otherwise, we will recommend a replacement for your safety.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Do you offer emergency services?<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes. We provide emergency tyre replacement and roadside assistance across London.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What areas do you cover?<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We cover all areas within Greater London, including central, north, east, west, and south regions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Do you work with businesses?<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes. We offer both one-time services and subscription-based plans for businesses and fleet operators.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Vision<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our goal is to become London\u2019s most trusted mobile tyre service provider.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We are building a system where tyre issues are no longer a major inconvenience. Instead, they become a quick, manageable situation handled by professionals who come directly to you.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We believe that convenience, speed, and trust should be the standard, not the exception.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Promise<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When you choose FixMyTyreNow, you are choosing:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>A reliable service you can count on<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>A team that values your time<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>A solution that puts your safety first<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>We are here to keep you moving, no matter where you are in London.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>About FixMyTyreNow Who We Are FixMyTyreNow was built with one clear mission: to make tyre emergencies, roadside breakdowns, and routine tyre replacements fast, simple, and completely stress-free across London. We understand that dealing with a flat tyre or damaged wheel is never convenient. It happens when you are rushing to work, picking up your children, [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-101","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/fixmytyrenow.com\/wp-j